dc_title_s: Boundaries of Planning Projects & Scanned Drawings: Howard County, Maryland
dc_description_s: The polygon boundaries of scanned plan drawings.  Each boundary is hyper-linked to a unique drawing in .PDF format.  The .PDF may be downloaded using this map layer.  Drawing types include: Capital Projects, ECPs, FDPs, Forest Conservation Plats, Plat Books, Plats By Number, Plats Of Survey, Preliminary, Preliminary Plans, Real Estate Service Plats, Receiving Plats, Record_Plats, Road And Supplemental Drawings, SDP, Signal Plans, Sketch Plans, Sketch Preliminary_Plans, SketchPlans, Survey Division Plats, and Watershed Restoration Projects.
